<H2>Cube</H2>
<H4 CLASS="st">Informations</H4>Author: <SCRIPT TYPE="text/javascript">document.write('<A H'+'REF="m'+'ailto:lsalvino'+'&#'+'64;'+'hotmail.com?subject=Cube">');</SCRIPT>Luciano Salvino<SCRIPT TYPE="text/javascript">document.write('<\/A>');</SCRIPT><BR>License: Freeware
<H4 CLASS="st">Description</H4>You can create a cube and rotate it around the x,y,z axes using the following function:<BR>
<BR>
<TT>Cube(<B>float</B> a, <B>float</B> b, <B>float</B> c, <B>float</B> scale, <B>float</B> alfax, <B>float</B> alfay, <B>float</B> alfaz)</TT><BR>
<BR>
where <TT>a</TT>, <TT>b</TT> and <TT>c</TT> are the cube dimensions; <TT>scale</TT> is the scaling factor; <TT>alfax</TT>, <TT>alfay</TT> and <TT>alfaz</TT> are the rotation angles.
